text: Salah Al-Humaidi (born December 1, 1974) is a Yemeni judoka, he competed internationally for Yemen at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==Career== Al-Humaidi was just 17 years old when he competed in the 60kg division at the 1992 Summer Olympics, he was drawn against Frenchman Philippe Pradayrol in round 32 in which he lost so didn't advance to the next round. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Yemeni male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Yemen Category:Judoka at the 1992 Summer Olympics
title: Salah Al-Humaidi
